org.fujion.plotly.plot

Class PlotSankey

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fujion.ancillary.Options
      • org.fujion.plotly.plot.PlotOptions
        • org.fujion.plotly.plot.PlotSankey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOptionMapTransform, IClientTransform

    public class PlotSankey
extends PlotOptions
    Options for sankey plot.

    A sankey plot is a type of flow diagram, in which the width of the link between two nodes is shown proportionally to the flow quantity.
